üß† Project Overview
This self-developed Power BI project focuses on building an end-to-end Sales Analytics Dashboard, highlighting key KPIs such as Sales, Profit %, LBS %, and Target Attainment.
The goal was to transform raw sales data into actionable business insights through efficient data modeling, DAX measures, and interactive visualization design.
